{"tid":225364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子把母猪當女朋友來養　天天抱著牠入睡","createTime":"2017-05-01T17:29:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T18:16:33.000Z","uid":87072,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6909042ac13ffcb282ef3e87affe88ed357f4648","tid":225364,"uid":87072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T17:29:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170502/640_f30f0b1a36d34c0e25eccdab4a8e5a4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170502%2F640_f30f0b1a36d34c0e25eccdab4a8e5a4b.jpg&h=c8cbcd41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名泰國男子養了一頭母豬將近1年，彼此培養出了深厚的感情，天天都抱著它睡覺。<br />\n據《泰國中文網》報導，一名泰國男子在Facebook上分享了他養的寵物豬照片，可愛的模樣迅速萌翻網友。男子表示，當初是在展場上買下牠，當時才3公斤重，店家雖然表示牠是長不大的寵物豬，但是10個月過去，小豬竟然胖到了100多公斤，「跟牠培養出感情了，所以不管牠怎麼胖、吃的怎麼多，我還是會繼續養」。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7SvaBV8ZEhQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7SvaBV8ZEhQ&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=fb7fb315\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7SvaBV8ZEhQ</a>"},{"pid":"11f14fc080593178fd49d23dea5407a921b5c86b","tid":225364,"uid":67418,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T17:32:27.000Z","msg":"都好阿 起馬唔會比女人背叛 人心不古阿"},{"pid":"331c7368aff1827a02be4a40a016847036ab2064","tid":225364,"uid":63950,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T17:35:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8dd5fce68dce98a7897ad36dcbf806bbb14b6205","tid":225364,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T17:35:33.000Z","msg":"佢地性生活如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f87e6d4e9643010b46a715f770cf9474156138","tid":225364,"uid":62822,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T17:36:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"30b42bf29078bf2700a93305fe37b30293e651ae","tid":2253